<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Welcome to Xingify</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 40px 20px;
        color: #333;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 40px 30px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }

      .logo {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }

      .logo h1 {
        color: #333;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      h2 {
        color: #222;
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .highlight {
        color: #333;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .footer {
        margin-top: 40px;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #888;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo">
        <h1>Xingify</h1>
      </div>

      <h2>Welcome to the club!</h2>
      <p>Hi there,</p>

      <p>
        You're now officially subscribed to receive updates from
        <span class="highlight">Xingify</span>. Get ready for exclusive early
        access to new arrivals, members-only deals, and limited edition drops.
      </p>

      <p>We’re thrilled to have you on board.</p>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px">— The Xingify Team</p>

      <div class="footer">
        You received this email because you subscribed on our website.
        <br />
        If you didn't do this, you can safely ignore this message.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
